description: More than a third of arrivals at Dublin Airport did not fill out a form detailing where they would be staying.
title: Coronavirus: Third of Dublin Airport passengers do not fill out isolation form
title_page: Coronavirus: Third of Dublin Airport passengers do not fill out isolation form - BBC News
maintext: Last week it was announced those over 70 in the country who have been cocooning in their homes because of Covid-19 can now go out and exercise, as part of a roadmap for lifting the current restrictions.
